\c 18
\s Ihubo likaDavida lokubonga uNkulunkulu ngokukhululwa
\d Kumqondisi wokuhlabelela. EsikaDavida, inceku yeN\nd kosi\nd*, eyakhuluma eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + Hlab. 36.\x* amazwi alelihubo mhla iN\nd kosi\nd* imkhulula esandleni sezitha zakhe zonke lesandleni sikaSawuli\x + 2 Sam. 22.1-51.\x*. Wasesithi:
\p
\v 1 Ngizakuthanda, N\nd kosi\nd*, mandla ami\x + Hlab. 116.1.\x*.
\v 2 IN\nd kosi\nd* ilidwala lami, lenqaba yami, lomkhululi wami; uNkulunkulu wami, idwala lami, engizaphephela kulo, isihlangu sami, lophondo losindiso lwami, inqaba yami ephakemeyo\x + Heb. 2.13.\x*.
\v 3 Ngizabiza iN\nd kosi\nd* edumisekayo, ngakho ngizasindiswa ezitheni zami.
\p
\v 4 Izibopho zokufa zangizingelezela, lezikhukhula zobubi zangethusa.
\v 5 Izibopho zesihogo zangigombolozela, imijibila yokufa yayiphambi kwami\x + Hlab. 17.13. 18.18. Mat. 17.25.\x*.
\v 6 Ekuhluphekeni kwami ngayibiza iN\nd kosi\nd*, ngakhala kuNkulunkulu wami; walizwa ilizwi lami esethempelini lakhe, lokukhala kwami kweza phambi kwakhe, endlebeni zakhe\x + Hlab. 66.14.\x*.
\p
\v 7 Khona umhlaba wazamazama, wanyikinyeka, lezisekelo zezintaba zaqhaqhazela, zazamazama, ngoba wayethukuthele\x + 2 Sam. 22.8.\x*.
\v 8 Kwenyuka intuthu emakhaleni akhe, lomlilo ophuma emlonyeni wakhe waqothula; amalahle avuthiswa yiwo\x + Hlab. 21.9.\x*.
\v 9 Wasekhothamisa amazulu, wehlela phansi, lomnyama onzima wawungaphansi kwenyawo zakhe.
\v 10 Wasegada \w ikherubhi\w**, waphapha, wandiza phezu kwempiko zomoya\x + Dute. 28.49.\x*.
\v 11 Wamisa umnyama \add waba\add* yindawo yakhe yensitha, idumba lakhe inhlangothi zonke zakhe, amanzi amnyama, amayezi amnyama omkhathi\x + 2 Sam. 22.12.\x*.
\v 12 Ekukhazimuleni okuphambi kwakhe amayezi akhe amnyama edlula, isiqhotho lamalahle omlilo\x + Josh. 10.11. 2 Sam. 22.13,14. Hlab. 148.8.\x*.
\v 13 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasiduma emazulwini, oPhezukonke wazwakalisa ilizwi lakhe, isiqhotho lamalahle omlilo\x + Josh. 10.11. 2 Sam. 22.13,14. Hlab. 148.8.\x*.
\v 14 Yasithuma imitshoko yayo, yabachitha; lemibane eminengi, yabaphaphathekisa.
\v 15 Khona kwabonakala imisele yamanzi, kwembulwa izisekelo zomhlaba ekusoleni kwakho\x + Hlab. 42.1. Jow. 1.20. Jobe 36.30.\x*, N\nd kosi\nd*, ekuvutheleni komoya wamakhala akho.
\p
\v 16 Yathuma iphezulu, yangibamba, yangenyula emanzini amanengi.
\v 17 Yangophula esitheni sami esilamandla, lakibo abangizondayo, ngoba babelamandla kulami\x + Hlab. 142.6.\x*.
\v 18 Babephambi kwami osukwini lwenhlupheko yami, kodwa iN\nd kosi\nd* yaba yisisekelo sami\x + Hlab. 17.13. 18.18. Mat. 17.25.\x*.
\v 19 Yangikhuphela endaweni ebanzi, yangikhulula ngoba yayithokoza ngami.
\p
\v 20 IN\nd kosi\nd* yangivuza njengokulunga kwami; yangibuyisela njengokuhlanzeka kwezandla zami.
\v 21 Ngoba ngizilondolozile indlela zeN\nd kosi\nd*, kangisukanga kuNkulunkulu wami ngenkohlakalo.
\v 22 Ngoba zonke izahlulelo zayo zaziphambi kwami, lezimiso zayo kangiziphambulanga kimi\x + 2 Sam. 22.23.\x*.
\v 23 Njalo ngangiqondile kuyo, ngizinqandile ebubini bami.
\v 24 Ngakho iN\nd kosi\nd* ingibuyisele njengokulunga kwami, njengokuhlanzeka kwezandla zami phambi kwamehlo ayo.
\p
\v 25 Kolesihawu uzaziveza ulesihawu; koqotho uzaziveza uqotho;
\v 26 kohlanzekileyo uzaziveza uhlanzekile; lakophambukileyo uzaziveza uphambukile.
\v 27 Ngoba wena uzabasindisa abantu abahlutshwayo; kodwa amehlo aphakemeyo uzawehlisela phansi\x + Zaga 6.17. 2 Sam. 22.28.\x*.
\v 28 Ngoba wena uzalumathisa isibane sami; iN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu wami, izakhanyisa ubumnyama bami.
\v 29 Ngoba ngawe ngigijimile \add ngadabula phakathi\add* kwebutho, langoNkulunkulu wami ngeqe umthangala.
\p
\v 30 UNkulunkulu, indlela yakhe iphelele; ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* lihloliwe; uyisihlangu kubo bonke abaphephela kuye.
\v 31 Ngoba ngubani onguNkulunkulu ngaphandle kweN\nd kosi\nd*? Njalo ngubani olidwala ngaphandle kukaNkulunkulu wethu?
\v 32 NguNkulunkulu ongibhincisa amandla\x + 2 Sam. 22.33.\x*\x + 1 Sam. 2.4.\x*, owenza indlela yami iphelele\x + 2 Sam. 22.33.\x*.
\v 33 Owenza inyawo zami zibe njenge\add ze\add*zimpala, wangimisa ezingqongeni zami.
\v 34 Ofundisela izandla zami impi, ukuze idandili lethusi ligotshiswe zingalo zami.
\v 35 Unginikile lesihlangu sosindiso lwakho, lesandla sakho sokunene\x + 2 Sam. 22.36.\x* singisekele\x + Hlab. 20.2.\x*, lobumnene bakho bungikhulisile.
\v 36 Wenze zaba banzi izinyathelo zami ngaphansi kwami, ukuze inyawo zami zingatsheleli.
\p
\v 37 Ngixotshene lezitha zami, ngazifica, kangibuyanga ngaze ngaziqeda.
\v 38 Ngazigwaza, zaze zehluleka ukuvuka, zawa ngaphansi kwenyawo zami.
\v 39 Ngoba ungibhincise amandla kusenzelwa impi, wabakhothamisela phansi kwami abangivukelayo.
\v 40 Unginike intamo yezitha zami, labo abangizondayo ngababhubhisa.
\v 41 Bakhala, kodwa engekho umsindisi; eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, kodwa kayibaphendulanga\x + Zaga 1.28. 2 Sam. 22.42.\x*.
\v 42 Ngasengibacholisisa njengothuli phambi komoya, ngabachitha njengodaka lwezitalada.
\p
\v 43 Wangikhulula ekuphikiseni kwabantu, wangimisa ngaba yinhloko yezizwe; abantu engangingabazi bangisebenzela.
\v 44 Bangenela ukuzwa ngendlebe bazangilalela, abezizweni bazazithoba kimi ngokuzenzisa.
\v 45 Abezizweni bazabuna, baphume ezinqabeni zabo bethuthumela.
\p
\v 46 IN\nd kosi\nd* iyaphila; njalo kalidunyiswe idwala lami, kaphakanyiswe uNkulunkulu wosindiso lwami.
\v 47 UNkulunkulu onginika impindiselo, lowehlisela izizwe ngaphansi kwami\x + Hlab. 47.3.\x*;
\v 48 ongikhulula ezitheni zami; yebo, phezu kwabangivukelayo wangiphakamisa, emuntwini wodlakela wangikhulula.
\v 49 Ngenxa yalokhu\x + Roma 15.9.\x* ngizakudumisa, N\nd kosi\nd*, phakathi kwezizwe, ngihlabelele ibizo lakho indumiso\x + Hlab. 42.5.\x*.
\v 50 Iyanika inkosi yayo usindiso olukhulu, isenzela ogcotshiweyo wayo umusa, kuDavida, lenzalweni yakhe kuze kube nininini\x + Hlab. 20.6.\x*.
